name: Petruk
description: Petruk is a clown character in Javanese wayang, on the side of the Witaradya lineage. Petruk is not mentioned in the Mahabharata from India. The existence of this figure in the world of wayang is an original composition of the Javanese people. In the Pasundan realm, Petruk is better known as Dawala or Udel.
